79265/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Transcatheter+therapeutic+embolization+of+multiple+coronary+artery+fistulas&amp;author=J+Vitek&amp;author=JW+Moses&amp;author=GS+Roubin&amp;author=MB+Leon&amp;author=N+Kipshidze&amp;publication_year=2001&amp;journal=Circulation&amp;pages=E19&amp;doi=10.1161%2Fhc3001.093607&amp;pmid=11479265">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></section></div></section></div><div class="core-collateral" role="dialog" aria-modal="true"><div id="core-collateral-info" data-active-pane="false"><header><h2><i class="icon-info" aria-hidden="true"></i>Information &amp; Authors</h2></header><section id="tab-information" role="tabpanel"><h3>Information</h3><section class="core-self-citation"><h4>Published In</h4><div class="core-journal-presentation">



        
