ani</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Hussam A Almalki</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Asim A Saati</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Saeed E Alzahrani</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Saleh M Khouj</span></li></ul></div><div class="meta">2023Jun30 | Cureus, Vol. 29</div></div><div class="getFTR external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.7759/cureus.41168">Crossref</a></div></div></li><li class="citedByEntry" data-doi="10.26599/1671-5411.2023.06.007"><div class="related"><div class="related__title"><a target="_blank" href="https://doi.org/10.26599/1671-5411.2023.06.007">Unraveling the mechanisms of a giant coronary sinus</a></div><div class="related__authors"><ul class="rlist--inline loa mobile-authors loa-height"><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Michail Kyrtsopoulos</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Apostolos Galatas</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Anastasios Kartas</span></li></ul></div><div class="meta">2023Jun1 | Journal of Geriatric Cardiology, Vol. 20, No. 6</div></div><div class="getFTR external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.26599/1671-5411.2023.06.007">Crossref</a></div></div></li><li class="citedByEntry" data-doi="10.1148/rg.220063"><div class="related"><div class="related__title"><a target="_self" href="/doi/full/10.1148/rg.220063">Cardiac Outpouchings: Practical Approach to Normal Variants and                     Pathologic Conditions at CT and MRI</a></div><div class="related__authors"><ul class="rlist--inline loa mobile-authors loa-height"><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Cameron Hassani</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Christopher M. Walker</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Felipe Urdaneta</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class